graph LR
    TrainingOp[Training Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    TrainingOp -->|container orchestration<br/>CRD management| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.27+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    TrainingOp -.->|webhook TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager]
    TrainingOp -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano[Volcano Scheduler]
    TrainingOp -.->|gang scheduling alt| SchedulerPlugins[scheduler-plugins]
    TrainingOp -.->|metrics collection| Prometheus[Prometheus]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ODHOperator[OpenDataHub Operator] -->|deploys & manages| TrainingOp
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI management<br/>job viewing| TrainingOp

    %% Training Job Dependencies
    TrainingOp -->|API server access| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    TrainingOp -->|image pulls| ContainerRegistry[Container Registries<br/>quay.io, docker.io]
    TrainingOp -->|datasets & checkpoints| S3[S3/Object Storage<br/>AWS S3, MinIO]

    %% Integration Points (CRD-based)
    subgraph "Training Job CRDs"
        PyTorchJob[PyTorchJob<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        TFJob[TFJob<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        MPIJob[MPIJob<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        XGBoostJob[XGBoostJob<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        JAXJob[JAXJob<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        PaddleJob[PaddleJob<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    end

    TrainingOp -->|manages| PyTorchJob
    TrainingOp -->|manages| TFJob
    TrainingOp -->|manages| MPIJob
    TrainingOp -->|manages| XGBoostJob
    TrainingOp -->|manages| JAXJob
    TrainingOp -->|manages| PaddleJob

    %% Gang Scheduling CRDs
    TrainingOp -.->|creates optional| PodGroup[PodGroup CRD<br/>Volcano/scheduler-plugins]
    Volcano -.->|schedules| PodGroup
    SchedulerPlugins -.->|schedules| PodGroup

    %% Created Resources
    subgraph "Created Kubernetes Resources"
        Pods[Pods<br/>Master/Workers]
        Services[Services<br/>Headless ClusterIP]
        ConfigMaps[ConfigMaps]
        ServiceAccounts[ServiceAccounts]
    end

    TrainingOp -->|creates| Pods
    TrainingOp -->|creates| Services
    TrainingOp -->|creates| ConfigMaps
    TrainingOp -->|creates| ServiceAccounts

    %% Python SDK Integration
    PythonSDK[Python SDK<br/>kubeflow-training] -->|creates jobs| PyTorchJob
    PythonSDK -->|creates jobs| TFJob
    PythonSDK -->|creates jobs| MPIJob

